ATE 

ATE(AHB_out)

Parameters

AHB_out:
file, Dataframe, required		 The output of a call to one of the AHB algorithms.

Returns

ATE:
numeric scalar		 A numeric sclar representing the estimated average treatment effect (ATE) for the matching data.
